HEADWORD: Copesmate
<hw>Copes"mate`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An associate or
companion; a friend; a partner.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Misshapen time, <qex>copesmate</qex> of ugly Night.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Copestone</ent>⟦br⟧
